description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20MIN full body pilates workout // DAY 1 CHALLENGE // no equipment' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
